{"id":588815,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【立此存照】人民日报疑误发怒怼川普英语推/","date":"2018-07-12T05:44:51Z","modified":"2018-07-12T05:44:51Z","title":"【立此存照】人民日报疑“误发”怒怼川普英语推文后删除","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>清华-卡内基全球政策中心的 Paul Haenle (@paulhaenle) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/paulhaenle/status/1017228787535220736\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">发现</a>，《人民日报》英语推号今日发布了一条怒怼川普的推文，<strong>指责美国“不要把自己的外交政策上的失败怪到中国头上”</strong>（图1）。<strong>这条内容随后很快被删除，据 Haenle 称只存活了大约9分钟。</strong>删除操作的一种可能是，相关工作人员接到了上级的电话指令。另一种<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LunaLinCN/status/1017231447701250049\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">可能则是</a>，这位推号管理员不小心将个人账号的内容发到了机构账号上。经搜索，确实也有一个推号在同一时间段内发表了同样的话（图2）。</p>\n<p>《人日》的英语推号长期以来都是一副岁月静好的形象，与墙内鸡血满满的“<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5-%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e5%8d%87%e7%ba%a7%e8%b4%b8%e6%98%93%e6%88%98%e6%98%af%e9%9c%b8%e5%87%8c%e4%b8%bb%e4%b9%89%e5%af%b9%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e7%9a%84%e6%8c%91/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">国运之战</a>”不可同日而语。这次无论是上级指令还是工作人员的误操作，<strong>党媒显然只在窝里横。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>图1：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588817\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/人日推号.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-588817\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/人日推号.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"295\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/人日推号.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/人日推号-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/人日推号-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/人日推号-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">图片来自：Twitter @paulhaenle</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>图2：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588818\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/疑似人日马甲.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-588818\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/疑似人日马甲.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"232\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/疑似人日马甲.jpg 1178w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/疑似人日马甲-300x133.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/疑似人日马甲-768x340.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/疑似人日马甲-1024x453.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">这个账号在同一时间段发表了与人日怒怼川普内容相同的推文；推特截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%ba%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e8%b6%8a%e5%bc%ba%e5%a4%a7%e7%9a%84%e4%ba%ba%e8%b6%8a%e6%80%82%ef%bc%9f/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【新闻连连看】人民日报的“怂之魔障” </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5-%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e5%8d%87%e7%ba%a7%e8%b4%b8%e6%98%93%e6%88%98%e6%98%af%e9%9c%b8%e5%87%8c%e4%b8%bb%e4%b9%89%e5%af%b9%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e7%9a%84%e6%8c%91/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">人民日报 | 美国升级贸易战是霸凌主义对世界的挑衅 </a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">China&#39;s People&#39;s Daily had a little fun &quot;trolling&quot; Donald Trump on Twitter this morning in Beijing, until some Chinese authority instructed PD to take the tweet down. The tweet was only up for 9 minutes. <a href=\"https://t.co/ZkebyiZxnj\">pic.twitter.com/ZkebyiZxnj</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Paul T. Haenle (@paulhaenle) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/paulhaenle/status/1017228787535220736?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 12, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><strong>附：“共克时艰”之水军评论展</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588840\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/支持评论.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-588840\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/支持评论.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1949\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/支持评论.jpg 1418w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/支持评论-77x300.jpg 77w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/支持评论-768x2993.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/支持评论-263x1024.jpg 263w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">网易评论截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[32327,9807,19125,8646,9481]}